            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/class" class="table-row-link">
            <div class="class-content">
              <h2 class="class-title">Why you must train</h2>
              <p class="class-description">
                Here BowTiedOx, 5x DeGen Island bodybuilding champion is going to teach you the basics of training and it's importance
                Here BowTiedOx, 5x DeGen Island bodybuilding champion is going to teach you the basics of training and it's importance
